        "summary": "Waterfall ICP Search",
        "description": "### ðŸ’° Cost: 1 Credit per result\n\nThis is the core engine for Account-Based Prospecting. Define an ICP hierarchy (e.g. CEO â†’ VP Sales), and BlitzAPI will search progressively through each level until a decision-maker is found.\n\n[See Country Codes List](/guide/reference/appendix#common-country-codes-list)\n\n#### How to use `cascade`\nThis parameter is an array of objects. Each object represents a search step:\n1.Â  **Level 1**: Search for C-Levels.\n2.Â  **Level 2**: Search for VPs.\n3.Â  **Level 3**: Search for Directors.",
